{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><i><strong>Hang in there, thirsty bird.</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It gets hot out in the desert. So what's a flightless chick to do but rely on the mercurial blessings of the clouds above? Hang in there, thirsty bird; the sands are alive, and you might just find an unlikely ally lurking beneath.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273230/extras/storm_interlude.png?t=1737070420\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A <strong>retro</strong>-ish <strong>rhythm</strong>-ish game about catching raindrops.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Dodge, weave, and catch with an unusual <strong>two-level control scheme.</strong> Use the rhythm of the skies to help your timing. Go with the flow and <strong>let your hands learn to work together.</strong> It feels a little like learning a musical instrument. This game is hard to master, but the levels are gentle -- <i><strong>you can do it!</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273230/extras/desert_interlude.png?t=1737070420\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Catchy little tunes</strong> to keep you in the zone.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Five environments (and counting!) each with its own unique mechanic and song, plus a harder version for challenge junkies. Plus, you can import custom levels, and write your own with the dead-simple BirdScript chart system! It's real easy, I promise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273230/extras/birdscript_interlude.png?t=1737070420\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273230/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737070420","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steam